title: Quincy Boogers
text:
Quincy Boogers (born 28 December 1995) is a Dutch <a href="association%20football">football</a> player who last played for <a href="FC%20Dordrecht">FC Dordrecht</a>.
Club career.
He made his professional debut in the <a href="Eredivisie">Eredivisie</a> for <a href="FC%20Dordrecht">FC Dordrecht</a> on 17 May 2015 in a game against <a href="AFC%20Ajax">AFC Ajax</a>.
